          "tz": 480
        },
        "committer": {
          "name": "Bobi Jam",
          "email": "bobijam.xu@intel.com",
          "date": "2013-03-08 03:09:37.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-2899 lod: get ldo_stripenr correctly",
        "message": "LU-2899 lod: get ldo_stripenr correctly\n\nCurrent code relies on lod_statfs_and_check() to count the number of\nactivated LOD targets, while lod::ldo_stripenr derivation happens\nbefore calling lod_statfs_and_check(), and that makes\nlod::ldo_stripenr not accurate.\n\nThis patch make sure lod_statfs_and_check() called before updating\n::ldo_stripenr. And if there is [de]activation happens on OST target,\nclient needs wait 2*lod_qos_maxage seconds to get accurate\nld_active_tgt_count number.\n\nSigned-off-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam.xu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I37bebc69f876dd68da609fb5180bc6db36f01e84\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
